{"tid":1146282,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"逆線車起勢猛砵　女司機心怯　乖乖讓步激嬲網民？","createTime":"2019-05-09T07:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T12:51:03.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"82f9a3e1712242f597c3baba8261326b07756456","tid":1146282,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"逆線車起勢猛砵 女司機心怯 乖乖讓步激嬲網民？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H9TWlu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H9TWlu&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=791a7de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H9TWlu</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190509/photo/bkn-20190509123235562-0509_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190509134810\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190509123235562-0509_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190509134810&h=c4bef8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行錯仲砵人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」發貼指，她於周三（8日）上午6時許，在豐順街近沙田培英中學行駛時，忽然見到迎面有私家車駛至，更不停響號，頓時把她嚇一大跳。<br />\n<br />\n她一度懷疑自己逆線行駛，連忙褪車：「我呢度入㗎嘛！我呢度出㗎咩？究竟邊個錯呀」。惟她事後醒覺，怒斥謂︰「你個X頭，入X錯線仲敢狂砵」。"},{"pid":"eef7c6c930f2ccd9a026cf2193446e2ea72e2f83","tid":1146282,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"正確黎講係咪應該自己入返後波走？"},{"pid":"73f2351596344ef627eb4e4384e534271052080d","tid":1146282,"uid":65470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"on9先讓<br />\n老HI都頂住佢 夠做埋黎等收錢"},{"pid":"a0db23b7fa6741a5b165bb6ae11ea37335ed67f7","tid":1146282,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"揸親呢d保姆車十個八個都痴痴地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12f79155dc431d69b0b25141d89b09a1e60c4b4","tid":1146282,"uid":196484,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.c